.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-8::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, pineapple, watermelon, zucchini
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, dancing, hiking, magic-tricks
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, prince, chaman, bolivar
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
4. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
8. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pineapple    | zucchini | broccoli    |
| Hobby         | hiking     | magic-tricks | dancing  | board-games |
| Cigar   | prince    | bolivar      | davidoff   | chaman         |

