3. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
7. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
8. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2       |     3      |   4    |
