3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the project-manager##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the teacher##3
5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the teacher##3
6. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the helicopter and the person watching spy movies##2
7. the person watching scientific movies is the project-manager##1
8. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre    | scientific   | sports   | spy    | mystery |
| Job         | project-manager | teacher    | nurse      | writer |
| Transport   | helicopter      | snowmobile | skateboard | bike   |

