.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-13::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, turtle, frog
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, traveling, woodworking, writing
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, scooter, snowmobile, train
1. the owner of the chinchilla is the person driving the car##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the owner of the goat and the person who's hobby is writing##2
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person driving the train##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
6. the owner of the goat is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
7. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
9. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Pet    | goat      | chinchilla | frog       | turtle  |
| Hobby       | woodworking | board-games | writing    | traveling |
| Transport   | scooter     | car         | snowmobile | train     |

