2. the person eating lettuce is the fan of disco##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
6. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
7. the person eating cabbage is the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
