.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, coffee, iced-tea, soy-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, journalist, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, skateboarding, surfing
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the bartender##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking iced-tea##2
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the journalist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Beverage    | iced-tea | coffee  | cola  | soy-milk           |
| Job     | bartender | journalist | dancer   | security-guard |
| Sport   | surfing   | golf       | biathlon | skateboarding  |

 